## 8. AI Agent Internal Graph

```mermaid
flowchart TD
  A["receive_message"] --> B["load_business_context"]
  B --> C["load_customer_profile"]
  C --> D["load_conversation_history"]
  D --> E["check_human_takeover"]

  E --> F{"Human takeover?"}
  F -->|"Yes"| G["stop_ai_reply<br/>notify admin"]
