  N -->|"payment"| Q["create_payment_qris_tool"]
  N -->|"handoff"| R["human_handoff_tool"]
  N -->|"knowledge"| S["knowledge_search_tool"]```mermaid


  O --> T["execute_tool via services/api"]
  P --> T
  Q --> T
  R --> T
  S --> T

  T --> U["save_state"]
  U --> L
  L --> V["return_reply_to_api"]
```

